      • REMOVE_ADD_TRUSTED_DEVICE_TC

        public void REMOVE_ADD_TRUSTED_DEVICE_TC()
                                  throws java.io.IOException
        Summary
        Remove and Add Trusted devices
        Pre-Conditions
        DashBoard page should be open
        User should have administrator rights
        Steps
        1. Click on Preferences
        2. Click on 'Trusted Devices'
        3. Click on Delete option of prefered device
        4. Logout from account
        5. Login again
        6. Click on OK button when Trusted Devices window appeared
        Expected Result:
        1. Verify that machine is deleted from the trusted devices and added again to trusted devices list
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - Signals that an I/O exception of some sort has occurred. This class is the general class of exceptions produced by failed or interrupted I/O operations.
